title: Making a Beautiful Garden with Squires Garden Centres DVDRip MP4
description:
Gardening remains one of the nation's true passions. Millions of us spend our weekends and summer evenings planning and planting in order to create our own special oasis.

This beautifully filmed DVD covers a whole range of gardening topics suitable for a variety of garden sizes. locations and types. Whether you have a small patio in a town, a brand new garden or more expansive acreage this DVD will have something for you to view and then use.

The advice is easy and practical to follow, given by real gardeners and presented by the renowned author Tom Petherick and covers the following areas:

Pots and containers
Ponds
Soil preparation
Planting borders
Vegetables
Rose pruning and care
Maintaining your lawn
